{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I love theater."},{"time":3000,"text":"I love the idea that you can transform, become somebody else"},{"time":6000,"text":"and look at life with a completely new perspective."},{"time":9000,"text":"I love the idea that people will sit in one room for a couple of hours and listen."},{"time":17000,"text":"The idea that in that room at that moment,"},{"time":19000,"text":"everyone, regardless of their age, their gender, their race, their color, their religion,"},{"time":26000,"text":"comes together."},{"time":28000,"text":"At that moment, we transcend space and time together."},{"time":32000,"text":"Theater awakens our senses and opens the door to our imagination."},{"time":37000,"text":"And our ability to imagine is what makes us explorers."},{"time":40000,"text":"Our ability to imagine makes us inventors and creators and unique."},{"time":46000,"text":"I was commissioned in 2003 to create an original show,"},{"time":51000,"text":"and began developing \"Upwake.\""},{"time":54000,"text":"\"Upwake\" tells the story of Zero,"},{"time":56000,"text":"a modern-day business man, going to work with his life in a suitcase,"},{"time":60000,"text":"stuck between dream and reality and not able to decipher the two."},{"time":65000,"text":"I wanted \"Upwake\" to have the same audiovisual qualities as a movie would."},{"time":69000,"text":"And I wanted to let my imagination run wild."},{"time":72000,"text":"So I began drawing the story that was moving in my head."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"If Antoine de Saint-Exupery, the author of \"The Little Prince,\" were here,"},{"time":84000,"text":"he would have drawn three holes inside that box"},{"time":86000,"text":"and told you your sheep was inside."},{"time":89000,"text":"Because, if you look closely enough, things will begin to appear."},{"time":92000,"text":"This is not a box; these are the renderings of my imagination"},{"time":95000,"text":"from head to paper to screen to life."},{"time":99000,"text":"In \"Upwake\" buildings wear suits, Zero tap dances on a giant keyboard,"},{"time":104000,"text":"clones himself with a scanner, tames and whips the computer mice,"},{"time":108000,"text":"sails away into dreamscape from a single piece of paper and launches into space."},{"time":113000,"text":"I wanted to create environments that moved and morphed like an illusionist."},{"time":117000,"text":"Go from one world to another in a second."},{"time":120000,"text":"I wanted to have humor, beauty, simplicity and complexity"},{"time":125000,"text":"and use metaphors to suggest ideas."},{"time":127000,"text":"At the beginning of the show, for example, Zero deejays dream and reality."},{"time":133000,"text":"Technology is an instrument that allowed me to manifest my visions"},{"time":137000,"text":"in high definition, live, on stage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140000,"text":"So today, I would like to talk to you about the relationship"},{"time":144000,"text":"between theater and technology."},{"time":147000,"text":"Let's start with technology."},{"time":150000,"text":"(Fuse blowing)"},{"time":154000,"text":"All right. Let's start with theater."},{"time":157000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":181000,"text":"(Buzzing)"},{"time":191000,"text":"(Click, click, bang)"},{"time":220000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":332000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":338000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"\"Upwake\" lasts 52 minutes and 54 seconds."},{"time":344000,"text":"I project 3D animation on all the four surfaces of the stage"},{"time":348000,"text":"which I interact with."},{"time":351000,"text":"The use of animation and projection was a process of discovery."},{"time":354000,"text":"I didn't use it as a special effect, but as a partner on stage."},{"time":359000,"text":"There are no special effects in \"Upwake,\" no artifice."},{"time":362000,"text":"It's as lavish and intricate as it is simple and minimal."},{"time":367000,"text":"Three hundred and forty-four frames, four and a half years and commissions later,"},{"time":372000,"text":"what started as a one person show became a collaborative work"},{"time":376000,"text":"of nineteen most talented artists."},{"time":378000,"text":"And here are some excerpts."},{"time":544000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":549000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"So this is, relatively, a new show that we're now beginning to tour."},{"time":554000,"text":"And in Austin, Texas,"},{"time":556000,"text":"I was asked to give small demonstrations in schools during the afternoon."},{"time":559000,"text":"When I arrived at one of the schools, I certainly did not expect this:"},{"time":564000,"text":"Six hundred kids, packed in a gymnasium, waiting."},{"time":567000,"text":"I was a little nervous performing without animation, costume -- really -- and make-up."},{"time":572000,"text":"But the teachers came to me afterward and told me"},{"time":575000,"text":"they hadn't seen the kids that attentive."},{"time":577000,"text":"And I think the reason why is that I was able to use their language and their reality"},{"time":581000,"text":"in order to transport them into another."},{"time":585000,"text":"Something happened along the way."},{"time":587000,"text":"Zero became a person and not just a character in a play."},{"time":590000,"text":"Zero does not speak, is neither man nor woman."},{"time":594000,"text":"Zero is Zero, a little hero of the 21st Century,"},{"time":598000,"text":"and Zero can touch so many more people than I possibly could."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603000,"text":"It's as much about bringing new disciplines inside this box"},{"time":607000,"text":"as it is about taking theater out of its box."},{"time":612000,"text":"As a street performer, I have learned that everybody wants to connect."},{"time":615000,"text":"And that usually, if you're a bit extraordinary, if you're not exactly of human appearance,"},{"time":620000,"text":"then people will feel inclined to participate and to feel out loud."},{"time":624000,"text":"It's as though you made something resonate within them."},{"time":627000,"text":"It's as though the mystery of the person they're interacting with and connecting"},{"time":631000,"text":"allows them to be themselves just a bit more."},{"time":634000,"text":"Because through your mask, they let theirs go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"Being human is an art form."},{"time":640000,"text":"I know theater can improve the quality of people's lives,"},{"time":642000,"text":"and I know theater can heal."},{"time":644000,"text":"I've worked as a doctor clown in a hospital for two years."},{"time":647000,"text":"I have seen sick kids and sad parents and doctors"},{"time":650000,"text":"be lifted and transported in moments of pure joy."},{"time":653000,"text":"I know theater unites us."},{"time":656000,"text":"Zero wants to engage the generation of today and tomorrow,"},{"time":660000,"text":"tell various stories through different mediums."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664000,"text":"Comic books. Quantum physics video games."},{"time":667000,"text":"And Zero wants to go to the moon."},{"time":669000,"text":"In 2007, Zero launched a green campaign,"},{"time":671000,"text":"suggesting his friends and fans to turn off their electricity"},{"time":675000,"text":"every Sunday from 7:53 to 8:00 p.m."},{"time":678000,"text":"The idea is simple, basic. It's not original,"},{"time":682000,"text":"but it's important, and it's important to participate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732000,"text":"There is a revolution."},{"time":735000,"text":"It's a human and technological revolution."},{"time":738000,"text":"It's motion and emotion."},{"time":740000,"text":"It's information."},{"time":742000,"text":"It's visual. It's musical. It's sensorial."},{"time":745000,"text":"It's conceptual. It's universal. It's beyond words and numbers."},{"time":748000,"text":"It's happening."},{"time":750000,"text":"The natural progression of science and art"},{"time":752000,"text":"finding each other to better touch and define the human experience."},{"time":757000,"text":"There is a revolution in the way that we think,"},{"time":759000,"text":"in the way that we share, and the way that we express our stories,"},{"time":764000,"text":"our evolution."},{"time":767000,"text":"This is a time of communication, connection and creative collaboration."},{"time":773000,"text":"Charlie Chaplin innovated motion pictures"},{"time":777000,"text":"and told stories through music, silence, humor and poetry."},{"time":785000,"text":"He was social, and his character, The Tramp, spoke to millions."},{"time":790000,"text":"He gave entertainment, pleasure and relief to so many human beings"},{"time":796000,"text":"when they needed it the most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799000,"text":"We are not here to question the possible; we are here to challenge the impossible."},{"time":805000,"text":"In the science of today, we become artists."},{"time":808000,"text":"In the art of today, we become scientists."},{"time":812000,"text":"We design our world. We invent possibilities."},{"time":816000,"text":"We teach, touch and move."},{"time":821000,"text":"It is now that we can use the diversity of our talents"},{"time":824000,"text":"to create intelligent, meaningful and extraordinary work. It's now."},{"time":831000,"text":"(Ringing)"},{"time":834000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":836000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}